lyrics:
[Verse]
In the deep, green forest, we gather round
With our mugs of beer, golden and brown
Under starlit sky, our laughter rings clear
Once every month, we jeer and cheer

[Chorus]
We meet to drink beer in the forest so grand
With the boys by the fire, a jolly band
Tales are spun, and memories are spun
As we dance and sing, till the night is done
